<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.9.5">
<l>ciṟappil vīṭu cuvarkka naraka</l>
<l>miṟappi leytuka veytaṟka yāṉum</l>
<l>piṟappil palpiṟa viperu māṉai</l>
<l>maṟappoṉ ṟiṉṟi yeṉṟu makiḻvēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In exultation let me reach liberation, heaven; hell</l>
<l>in death let me not reach, and I,</l>
<l>when born, in many births I will always rejoice,</l>
<l>without any forgetfulness, in the great lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
